[
  {
    "key": "ap4_6_3",
    "wrappers": [
      "title-div"
    ],
    "templateOptions": {
      "expressionLock": "formState.memoria.tipoMemoria.id === 3",
      "label": "4.6.3 Academic link with the research team"
    },
    "hideExpression": "!formState.mainModel.ap4_6.estudiantesSujetosInvestigacionRadio || formState.mainModel.ap4_6.estudiantesSujetosInvestigacionRadio === 'no'",
    "fieldGroup": [
      {
        "template": "<p>Will the students who participate have an academic link with the research team?</p>"
      },
      {
        "key": "vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio",
        "type": "radio",
        "templateOptions": {
          "label": "Choose an option:",
          "required": true,
          "options": [
            {
              "value": "no",
              "label": "No"
            },
            {
              "value": "si",
              "label": "Yes"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "template": "Please specify what this connection is and justify the need for that choice",
        "hideExpression": "!model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio || model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio !== 'si'"
      },
      {
        "key": "especificarVinculacion",
        "type": "textarea",
        "hideExpression": "!model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio || model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio !== 'si'",
        "templateOptions": {
          "label": "Please specify",
          "placeholder": "Please specify",
          "required": true,
          "autosize": true,
          "autosizeMinRows": "1",
          "autosizeMaxRows": "10"
        }
      },
      {
        "template": "<p>What special measures will be adopted to protect the voluntary nature of students academically linked to the research team?</p>",
        "hideExpression": "!model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio || model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio !== 'si'"
      },
      {
        "wrappers": [
          "info-div"
        ],
        "template": "<p>It is important to minimise the possible influence on the students at the time of recruitment, both by the teaching staff and by the pressure exerted by the group.</p><ul><li><strong>Direct recruitment:</strong> It is what the teacher does in the classroom or speaking with the students, offering academic incentives, etc. It is the least recommended, since coercion occurs.</li><li><strong>Interposition of a third person not academically linked to the students:</strong> When direct recruitment is necessary, it is recommended that it is not the teacher who carries out the recruitment, but rather a third person with no connection to the students.</li><li><strong>Indirect recruitment:</strong> through advertisements, brochures, etc.</li></ul>",
        "hideExpression": "!model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio || model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio !== 'si'"
      },
      {
        "template": "<p>Measures</p>",
        "hideExpression": "!model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio || model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio !== 'si'"
      },
      {
        "key": "medidasEspecialesEquipoInvestigadorRadio",
        "type": "radio",
        "hideExpression": "!model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio || model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio !== 'si'",
        "className": "vertical-radio",
        "required": true,
        "templateOptions": {
          "label": "Options:",
          "options": [
            {
              "value": "reclutamientoIndirecto",
              "label": "Indirect recruitment: Make sure it is described in section 3.4.1"
            },
            {
              "value": "interposicionTerceraPersona",
              "label": "Interposition of a third person to obtain consent, store personal data and encode it, direct contact with the student when carrying out tests or experiments. Identify and provide a descriptive document of your tasks and a commitment signature to carry them out if applicable. Please describe in section 3.4.1"
            },
            {
              "value": "otras",
              "label": "Others"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "template": "Please specify",
        "hideExpression": "!model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio || model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio !== 'si' || !model.medidasEspecialesEquipoInvestigadorRadio || model.medidasEspecialesEquipoInvestigadorRadio !== 'otras'"
      },
      {
        "key": "especificarOtras",
        "type": "textarea",
        "hideExpression": "!model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio || model.vinculacionAcademicaEquipoInvestigadorRadio !== 'si' || !model.medidasEspecialesEquipoInvestigadorRadio || model.medidasEspecialesEquipoInvestigadorRadio !== 'otras'",
        "templateOptions": {
          "label": "Please specify",
          "placeholder": "Please specify",
          "required": true,
          "autosize": true,
          "autosizeMinRows": "1",
          "autosizeMaxRows": "10"
        }
      },
      {
        "template": "<p>Is any member of the research team going to grade the students?</p>"
      },
      {
        "key": "calificacionEstudiantesRadio",
        "type": "radio",
        "templateOptions": {
          "label": "Choose an option:",
          "required": true,
          "options": [
            {
              "value": "no",
              "label": "No"
            },
            {
              "value": "si",
              "label": "Yes"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  }
]